{"tid":627507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用完即棄，無得詐形！警向人肉路障司機發「擬控告通知書」","createTime":"2018-04-13T04:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T18:15:20.000Z","uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b732b690d87da421514b360d3bc665c9fe0dae78","tid":627507,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180413/large/1523593733_76ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180413%2Flarge%2F1523593733_76ce.png&h=cfe9186f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方今年2月在粉嶺公路追截車輛時，疑截停市民車輛作人肉路障，導致2死6傷。立法會議員涂謹申指，警方最新向當時依照警方指示停車的司機發出「擬控告通知書」，形容警方做法「無腦」，「係你叫人停㗎嘛，係咪冇腦㗎？呢單嘢邊有可能告佢？」<br />\n<br />\n他解釋，一般已報警的交通意外，在未知誰是誰非的情況下，警方會向有可能起訴的人士發出通知書，「好似甲乙兩者撞車，兩個都會畀。根據法例諗住有可能告，就會畀你」，但他指今次事件是非已很清楚，傳媒播出的片段亦清晰見到司機是按指示停車。<br />\n<br />\n涂認為警方絕對可以決定不向被當作人肉路障的司機發出「擬控告通知書」，亦不應該發出，批評警方「一本通書睇到老」，罔顧事件中司機感受，「你就循例，人哋（涉事司機）唔識㗎嘛，會驚㗎嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180413/58067807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58067807&d=PIP6CtNqzdV40iPEgTS2v0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=b07ccaf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58067807&h=0bd36f7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180413/58067807</a>"},{"pid":"00314543d62d6584b5d53c6166962e82455bc8f7","tid":627507,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:41:01.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】今年7月警方徵用市民汽車阻截非法賽車，事<span style=\"color: red;\">後警務處處長鄧竟成公開道歉及承諾跟進賠償問題，但事隔三個月，車輛被毀的車主仍未獲賠償。當日的士被撞上壆的車主黃永祖批評，警方拖延賠償，更向維修車行施壓，提出「零件用得返就用」，將原本15萬元的維修費壓至11萬元</span>。有保險業人士指出，一般市民處理索償應透過公證行交涉，若警方直接干預，存在利益衝突。<br />\n記者：陳沛敏　許偉賢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20091022/large/22la6p2n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20091022%2Flarge%2F22la6p2n.jpg&h=45396daa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ea752cadcb4902d346427f742dcbdf563f066d5","tid":627507,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"涂謹申要求警犬用腦思考真係做得太過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8715b1610b5a412294ee66bf8111fceaf6695f62","tid":627507,"uid":22390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"警犬係咪真係小小法律知識都冇？"},{"pid":"1d0d4383a71a028be445d1263531589c460a3146","tid":627507,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"不如批准黑警入職個陣拎埋傷殘津貼啦，個撚個都智障嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037f464406462dff3e54f015560a1c50eeb4cfb0","tid":627507,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"車主有無話chok 親條頸"},{"pid":"84c8abba6b293b8fc3b906836d50609baa889e63","tid":627507,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ea752cadcb4902d346427f742dcbdf563f066d5","tid":627507,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"涂謹申要求警犬用腦思考真係做得太過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:50:22.000Z","msg":"阿 sir 用屎忽思考唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8352b13f2d34fe39064ff2b952da398766962eb6","tid":627507,"uid":147380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"比警犬搞到撞點解唔返原廠整?  搞到人撞車仲有資格講價?  屌你老母即刻頸痛腰痛玩大佢"},{"pid":"642a20d7b5851704100d5316e5bb8fee2ba34a4d","tid":627507,"uid":76471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:15:20.000Z","msg":"此 為 <span style=\"color: red;\">法 律 規 定</span> ， 因 日